  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study of the correlation between AGEsP and HbA1c and diabetic retinopathy prevalence:
      determination of cut-off value of AGEsP and HbA1c in type 2 diabetes diagnosis in China
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To find the cut-off point of AGEsP and HbA1c for diagnosis of diabetes by drawing the
      logistic regression model between prevalence of retinopathy and AGEsP level and HbA1c
      level,and find the point where the prevalence of retinopathy changes most rapidly.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
